{"tid":1361782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[689] 梁振英指不出動駐軍前提是幕後破壞勢力馬上收手","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T17:01:38.000Z","uid":249945,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80354c2fdfe06c9739c48bbbcd5785c08c2b947b","tid":1361782,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190725_20190725-003055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190725_20190725-003055.jpg&h=8db2f96f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全國政協副主席、前行政長官梁振英在社交網站帖文指，過去一個多月，暴徒圍堵警察總部，繼而攻入立法會大樓；然後得寸進尺，衝擊中聯辦，塗黑國徽，沒有人相信暴徒的上面沒有主腦，背後沒有金主。他和絕大多數香港人一樣，希望基本法關於解放軍駐港部隊執行任務的條文，繼續備而不用，希望香港警察可以有效控制局面，但前提是這些台前幕後的破壞勢力必須馬上收手，停止打擊警隊，停止一切暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英又指，解放軍駐港部隊根據基本法規定和程序，在必要時在香港履行職務，包括協助維持社會治安，並不是間接宣布一國兩制死亡，沒有人願意見到解放軍駐港部隊在街上執勤，但這並不等於說維護國家領土和主權完整，和社會治安的武裝力量形同虛設。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1143590&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1143590%26csid%3D261_341&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0A9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=2bb09e6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1143590&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"9a7723ed35f1349d5adec0aa1d8fe263511ea5e3","tid":1361782,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80354c2fdfe06c9739c48bbbcd5785c08c2b947b","tid":1361782,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190725_20190725-003055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190725_20190725-003055.jpg&h=8db2f96f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全國政協副主席、前行政長官梁振英在社交網站帖文指，過去一個多月，暴徒圍堵警察總部，繼而攻入立法會大樓；然後得寸進尺，衝擊中聯辦，塗黑國徽，沒有人相信暴徒的上面沒有主腦，背後沒有金主。他和絕大多數香港人一樣，希望基本法關於解放軍駐港部隊執行任務的條文，繼續備而不用，希望香港警察可以有效控制局面，但前提是這些台前幕後的破壞勢力必須馬上收手，停止打擊警隊，停止一切暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英又指，解放軍駐港部隊根據基本法規定和程序，在必要時在香港履行職務，包括協助維持社會治安，並不是間接宣布一國兩制死亡，沒有人願意見到解放軍駐港部隊在街上執勤，但這並不等於說維護國家領土和主權完整，和社會治安的武裝力量形同虛設。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1143590&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1143590%26csid%3D261_341&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0A9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=2bb09e6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1143590&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"df22a0e9d65bf24ab4d33f3c75eac4ea0e0a3973","tid":1361782,"uid":59633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:37:43.000Z","msg":"元朗無暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3880d89d1754b6472970f222db5759ea0aecc72d","tid":1361782,"uid":60749,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:38:50.000Z","msg":"得啦唔好講咁撚多<br />\n係出就快<br />\n唔出就縮返入老母閪唔好咁多嗲"},{"pid":"541f297352e71d0cd26eea7c1ccbcc074c6dd942","tid":1361782,"uid":7078,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snNgVoF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnNgVoF.gif&h=26e8e1a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbf87d367241bbdba45742925244dad4fac892a2","tid":1361782,"uid":5591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:44:52.000Z","msg":"老解原來係睇你689頭既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15fbdfb4679cdee4e9769d5c3332874d51f49b3a","tid":1361782,"uid":5343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:45:55.000Z","msg":"支持解放軍出馬，驅趕外國勢力，見一個鬼佬打一個，見兩個鬼佬就打一雙。等外國資金企業撒出香港，還我中國河山！！<img s